invalid type: string "Opening, Middlegame, and Endgame\nOpening:\nThe first phase where players develop pieces and control the center.\nMiddlegame:\nPlayers create tactics, attack pieces, and improve position.\nEndgame:\nFew pieces remain and the focus is promoting pawns and checkmating the king.\nFamous Chess Players:\n\u{7f} Garry Kasparov\n\u{7f} Magnus Carlsen\n\u{7f} Bobby Fischer", expected 